item.title: How To Find The Commands Of My Server
item.dc:creator: @Jessekinss Jessekinss
item.description:
@Jessekinss wrote:

[quote="[A"]mpd link=topic=378721.msg2851188#msg2851188 date=1246554399]

Sure.

Ok you right click your source and click delete (this is the easiest way to find it). After that, go into your recycling bin and delete it from there. Next you unplug your computer (and the most important part) you throw it out the window.

Wow Jesse, you are so hilarious! It would be great if MoparScape had more “comedic geniuses” like you! :)[/quote]

DUDE! For some reason I’m not I’m not seeing any sarcasm!
